description: Amundi S&P World Energy Screened UCITS ETF - EUR (A) seeks to replicate, as closely as possible, whether the trend is rising or falling, the performance of the S&P World Energy Weighted & Screened Index (the "Index"), and to minimize the tracking error between the net asset value of the Sub-Fund and the performance of the Index. The anticipated level of tracking error, under normal market conditions, is indicated in the prospectus of the Sub-Fund. For further information, please refer to the fund prospectus or KID.
